#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.where"
msgstr "# triton.language.where"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:4
msgid "简介：根据条件进行判断返回的是张量x还是y的值，条件为真时，返回x的值，否则返回y的值。"
msgstr "Introduction: Based on the condition, it returns the value of tensor x or y. If the condition is true, it returns the value of x; otherwise, it returns the value of y."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.where(condition, x, y, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `condition`        | `tensor(bool)`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `y`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `condition`   | `tensor(bool)`    | Tensor data |\n"
"| `x`           | `tensor`          | Tensor data |\n"
"| `y`           | `tensor`          | Tensor data |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`out`：输出张量的shape与输入x的shape相同\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`out`: The shape of the output tensor is the same as the shape of the input `x`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √     | √      | √     | √      |  √      |  √       |  √       | √      | √    | √   | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | √    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √     | √      | √     | √      |  √      |  √       |  √       | √      | √    | √   | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | √    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:22
msgid "结论：Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 uint、fp64 类型支持。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint and fp64 types compared to GPU."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:26
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3| 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5-dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:32
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:34
msgid "Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 uint、fp64 类型支持。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint and fp64 types compared to GPU."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:38
msgid "以下示例根据条件 `X < Y` 逐元素选择：条件为真时取 `X` 的元素，否则取常量 `1`。"
msgstr "The following example selects element-wise based on the condition `X < Y`: when the condition is true, it takes the element from `X`, otherwise it takes the constant `1`."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/where.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def fn_npu_(output_ptr, x_ptr, y_ptr, z_ptr,\n"
"            XB: tl.constexpr, YB: tl.constexpr, ZB: tl.constexpr,\n"
"            XNUMEL: tl.constexpr, YNUMEL: tl.constexpr, ZNUMEL: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    xoffs = tl.program_id(0) * XB\n"
"    yoffs = tl.program_id(1) * YB\n"
"    zoffs = tl.program_id(2) * ZB\n"
"\n"
"    xidx = tl.arange(0, XB) + xoffs\n"
"    yidx = tl.arange(0, YB) + yoffs\n"
"    zidx = tl.arange(0, ZB) + zoffs\n"
"\n"
"    idx = xidx[:, None, None] * YNUMEL * ZNUMEL + yidx[None, :, None] * ZNUMEL + zidx[None, None, :]\n"
"\n"
"    X = tl.load(x_ptr + idx)\n"
"    Y = tl.load(y_ptr + idx)\n"
"\n"
"    tmp2 = X < Y\n"
"    ret = tl.where(tmp2, X, 1)\n"
"\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + idx, ret)\n"
"\n"
"x = test_common.generate_tensor(shape, dtype).npu()\n"
"y = test_common.generate_tensor(shape, dtype).npu()\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

